WEBVTT

00:09:57.923 --> 00:10:02.125
One recalled that he probably
had more nerve-block injections

00:10:02.149 --> 00:10:04.727
than anyone else on the planet.

00:10:06.043 --> 00:10:09.481
Already a workaholic,
he worked even more --

00:10:09.505 --> 00:10:11.451
15- to 18-hour days.

00:10:11.922 --> 00:10:14.431
Healing others became more
than just his job,

00:10:14.455 --> 00:10:17.177
it was his own most effective
form of relief.

00:10:18.510 --> 00:10:22.321
"If I wasn't as busy as I am,"
he told a reporter at the time,

00:10:22.345 --> 00:10:25.530
"I would be a completely disabled guy."

00:10:27.423 --> 00:10:30.962
On a business trip to Florida
in the early 1980s,